### ArtyVoiceBot API Test File
### Use this with VS Code REST Client extension or copy to Postman

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:9441
@meetingUrl = https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meetup-join/YOUR_MEETING_URL_HERE

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/meeting/health

### Join a Meeting
# @name joinMeeting
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/meeting/join
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "joinUrl": "{{meetingUrl}}",
  "displayName": null
}

### Get Active Calls
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/meeting/active

### Leave a Meeting
# Replace CALL_ID with actual call ID from join response
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/meeting/leave
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "callId": "CALL_ID_HERE"
}

### Get All Audio Files
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/audio/files

### Download Specific Audio File
# Replace FILENAME with actual filename from files list
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/audio/download?filename=FILENAME_HERE

### Callback Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/callback/health

